        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12">
              <h4 class="heading">About Bitcoin Scripts</h4>
              <p class="heading__sub">
                Scripting languages date back from thousands of years ago. Mathematic formulae are an example of scripting language. <br />Bitcoin scripts use a specialized <a href="https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Script#Words" target="blank">scripting language</a> to write secure smart contracts and complex transactions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div> <!-- / .row -->
