      <div class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row"> 
            <div class="row-same-height">
              <div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-height col-middle">
                <h4 class="heading heading_left">A Stack-based Scripting System</h4>
                <p class="heading__sub">
                  Bitcoin uses a scripting system for complex transactions. Forth-like, Script is stack-based: instructions are <a href="<%= page_path('op_codes') %>" >1-byte opcodes</a> processed from left to right to be pushed on top of the stack sequentially, left-most first. All values are variable length byte arrays. Script is not Turing-complete, with no loops, for optimal security.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-sm-7 col-sm-height col-middle">
				<%= image_tag "stack_image.gif", class: "img-responsive" %>
              </div>
            </div> <!-- / .row-same-height -->
          </div> <!-- / .row -->
        </div> <!-- / .container -->
      </div> <!-- / .section -->


