                      <div class="portfolio-item-mask__summary">
                        This very simple script sets an expiry date and public key that must be matched to unlock the funds. The funds cannot move from the time locked address until the set expiry date and time. After the expiry, a single private key is required.
                      </div>
                    </div> <!-- / .portfolio-item-mask__content -->
