                    <div class="portfolio-item-mask__content">
                      <div class="portfolio-item-mask__title">
                        Contract Oracle
                      </div>
                      <div class="portfolio-item-mask__summary">
                        An external data source can be linked to a P2SH address with a certain value set in the script. The script requires two keys to unlock the funds, one key held by the beneficiary, the other key held by a trusted Oracle whose job is to validate that the value conditions are met.
                      </div>
