              <h4 class="heading">Lightning Network: a compelling use case for Bitcoin scripts</h4>
              <p class="heading__sub">
                The Lightning Network white paper ( draft version 0.5.9.1 dated November 20, 2015) describes a decentralized network for scalable, efficient payment channels. Transactions are sent over this routing network of micropayment channels whose transfer of value occurs off-blockchain. Bitcoin scripts enable time locked and hash locked transactions so that the payment protocol between users, via any number of Lightning Network hubs, remains trustless. This white paper by Joseph Poon and Thaddeus Dryja is probably the most important contribution since the invention of Bitcoin.
              </p>
              <a href="<%= products_path('product.pdf') %>" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary heading__btn wow fadeInUp" >Download White Paper</a>
